{"root":{"data":{"id":"dhtbyjlmo1s0","created":1776215821431,"text":"navigation_transport.launch"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhte59aqt7k0","created":1776221989774,"text":"navigation_transport_node","layout_right_offset":{"x":3.000000763030016,"y":-1138.9999986243965},"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhtk38n6co00","created":1776238758280,"text":" self.create_service(SetPose2D, '~/pick', self.start_pick_srv_callback) \n #创建服务，供外部调用导航抓取点的接口\n此处暂未使用，可能在语音指令处调用","priority":null,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhtle15z6hc0","created":1776242425118,"text":"回调函数：start_pick_srv_callback(self, request, response):\n主要功能：等待客户端发送一个目标点的欧拉角坐标发送过来，然后转换这个坐标为，最后再这个坐标上插上旗子","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhtpi2ixojs0","created":1776254025976,"text":"发布话题：self.mark_pub.publish(markerArray)\n话题类型：path_point\n功能： 把旗子发给 RViz 显示出来","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhtpi6xb0qo0","created":1776254035551,"text":"发布话题：self.nav_pub.publish(pose)  \n话题类型：self.nav_goal\n 功能：发布这个目标坐标","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhtkkjjxwjk0","created":1776240114220,"text":"self.create_service(SetPose2D, '~/place', self.start_place_srv_callback)\n #创建服务端，供外部调用导航放置点的接口\n客户端在：automatic_pick.py","priority":1,"layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhtle15z6hc0","created":1776242425118,"text":"回调函数：start_place_srv_callback(self, request, response)\n主要功能：等待客户端发送一个目标点的欧拉角坐标发送过来，然后转换这个坐标为，最后再这个坐标上插上旗子","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhtpi2ixojs0","created":1776254025976,"text":"发布话题：self.mark_pub.publish(markerArray)\n话题类型：path_point\n功能： 把旗子发给 RViz 显示出来","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhtpi6xb0qo0","created":1776254035551,"text":"发布话题：self.nav_pub.publish(pose)  \n话题类型：self.nav_goal\n 功能：发布这个目标坐标","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhtm7iub7dc0","created":1776244736155,"text":"self.create_subscription(PoseStamped, self.nav_goal, self.goal_callback, 1, callback_group=timer_cb_group)\n订阅话题类型  ：self.nav_goal\n功能：#订阅导航目标点话题，供外部调用\n回调函数：goal_callback","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhtpzy6xyko0","created":1776255427097,"text":"回调函数：goal_callback(self, msg)"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhtq2pfqixk0","created":1776255643130,"text":"1、查询当前为抓取或者放置状态"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhtq3arw18o0","created":1776255689578,"text":"2、根据状态调整pick和False的状态，随后发送导航目标点"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhtq4fb31xc0","created":1776255777810,"text":"3、监控导航进度，阻塞运行，做超时处理"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dhtq52pj9ls0","created":1776255828749,"text":"4、到晚完毕判断状态"},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhte5ie2lrk0","created":1776222009566,"text":"automatic_pick_launch","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhte6ajp7yo0","created":1776222070856,"text":"automatic_pick","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhtli6mgb5s0","created":1776242750455,"text":"self.transport_client = self.create_client(SetPose2D, '/navigation_transport/place')\n #创建服务客户端，用于在拾取完成后将放置位置发送给导航模块，以便导航模块能够引导机器人前往正确的放置位置","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhte64idxjc0","created":1776222057716,"text":"navigation_launch","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhte6gbh8740","created":1776222083420,"text":"bringup.launch","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dhtpuu2ape80","created":1776255026288,"text":"rviz_node\n启动Rviz","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dhtpvm04wbc0","created":1776255087108,"text":"通过\"Nav2 Goal\" 按钮\n\n发布话题：nav_goal","layout":null},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"classic","version":"1.4.43"}